Sentencas: Various compositions in the Ag-CuO(x) system are being investigated as potential filler metals for use in air brazing high-temperature electrochemical devices such as solid oxide fuel cells and gas concentrators.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx

Sentencas: Prior work has shown that the melting temperature, and therefore the potential operational temperature, of these materials can be increased by alloying with palladium.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx

Sentencas: The current study examines the effects of palladium addition on the joint strength of specimens prepared from yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) bars brazed with three different families of filler metals: Ag-CuO, 5Pd-Ag-CuO, and 15Pd-Ag-CuO.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx

Sentencas: In general, it was found that palladium leads to a small-to-moderate decrease in joint strength, particularly in low copper oxide containing filler metals.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx

Sentencas: However, the declination in strength is likely an acceptable trade-off for increased use temperature.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx

Sentencas: In addition, a critical composition was observed for each filler metal series at which the mechanism for joint failure underwent a transition, typically from ductile to brittle failure.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx

Sentencas: In each case, this composition corresponds approximately to the silver-rich boundary composition of the liquid miscibility gap in each system at the temperature of brazing.
Titulo: Effect of filler metal composition on the strength of yttria stabilized zirconia joints brazed with Pd-Ag-CuOx
